","tid":574811,"uid":45788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T17:54:53.000Z","msg":"樓主你好Gay"},{"pid":"2d46e61aa1c878f27030c54e61469ada1abd5d27","tid":574811,"uid":99386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T17:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你好Gay</blockquote><br />\n點解咁覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1b6b1323e1ac22590f763acfc1a6a456d1e26a","tid":574811,"uid":132210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:00:38.000Z","msg":"一齊去食下好野 做啲on9氹到笑就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲女鐘意呻咪聽 九成時候都係純粹想呻下 唔係要建議 如果要建議既 其實佢地好多時都心中有數<br />\n令佢感受到你有用心聽佢講 表示支持 係佢身邊就夠<br />\n道理好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec3935caf168407fca684198852a68210b75a33","tid":574811,"uid":99386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:00:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽我呻 認同我 做啲無聊野氹下我笑俾我輕鬆下<br />\n就算覺得我煩都唔好表露俾我睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係佢份人真係玻璃心到一個點，就算氹完佢，只要收左線一陣冇搵佢，講緊兩三個鐘，佢就會覺得你唔關心佢<br />\n<br />\n好似之前佢病左，純粹口嚨痛，已經keep住問佢有冇食藥、仲有冇唔舒服、休息多啲呀咁，問到我都嫌自己有啲煩，漏左一次冇問，佢就話我問都唔問下佢好啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43267ea70c4c51485dd30a07c5841db288f01f3","tid":574811,"uid":84472,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:02:05.000Z","msg":"你要問即係你唔夠愛佢"}]}